  "body": "<p>Perhaps you've heard the news... </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605511533687-RIIYT0TF43Q17EOJXTAX/7a-twopeasscreenshot.png\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Thank you so much to those who have already tweeted or sent me messages. So excited and grateful to join a talented group of ladies known as the Garden Girls on <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/whats-hot/\">Two Peas</a>. <a href=\"http://www.amyheller.typepad.com/\">Amy Heller</a>, <a href=\"http://www.wilnaf.com/\">Wilna Furstenberg</a> and I were given such a warm welcome last week. When I first started scrapbooking in 2007, <a href=\"http://embers.typepad.com/\">Emily Falconbridge</a> introduced me to the hobby, products and the <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/whats-hot/\">website</a>. I was completely smitten and still am. Here's a 2-pager that I did for my first layout using photos from Madame Tussauds. </p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605511550974-7W7L22ORPFG4I656N9O3/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.twopeasinabucket.com/gallery/member/305620-amytangerine/1789447-some-familiar-faces/\">copyright Two Peas in A Bucket</a></p><p>If you've never been to <a href=\"http://www.madametussauds.com/\">Madame Tussauds</a>, it's quite a treat. </p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"7c-dsc_04382.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605511569533-06X5GREBHAQJW8A50XDU/7c-dsc_04382.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"7d-dsc_2028.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605511569491-P3R50ZSQXLY7UTZIHUUW/7d-dsc_2028.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n\n\n<p>Another treat is celebrating with all of you! <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/whats-hot/\"><strong>Two Peas in a Bucket</strong></a><strong> is kindly giving free shipping for orders over $35. The coupon code is ATFS35 and should be entered at checkout.</strong> Here are the details: The user will receive free shipping on domestically shipped orders when  his/her total is $35 or greater in non-digital/non-phaseout product.  International customers will receive a $5 discount on shipping expenses. Promo code will expire on 1/20/12 at 11:59pm CST.</p><p>PS- I just noticed that The Little Things Daybook is already sold out, but the 3 other new ones are still in stock. <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/_amy%2520tangerine_/%3Fpp%3D300\">Happy shopping!</a></p>"
}